data.description: Opportunity awaits you in this 4 BR 3.5 BA one owner home nestled in the heart of Coronado!  Interior has been freshly painted so you’ll have a clean slate to start from.  Updated kitchen opens to a family room & breakfast area and features granite counters, stainless steel appliances & pantry space galore! The formal dining and living room with fireplace provide ample space for entertainment. Primary suite boasts a walk in closet, deep tub & private deck that overlooks a floral arrangement of jasmine, roses,bird of paradise & a stunning magnolia tree. Back bedroom has a private deck that overlooks the new deck. Built-ins along the upper hallway insure you’ll have plenty of space for storage or display.  Home is fully fenced with an inground sprinkler system. 2 car garage with alley access means parking is a breeze.  All that Coronado has to offer can be easily accessed, or simply sit back and enjoy the comfort of it all from the privacy of your own home conveniently located home and the lifestyle you’ve been dreaming of.Your next chapter starts here.
